  "title": "Cafe server / barista",
  "description": "<p>An energetic, fun and vibrant working environment in a cafe situated on the Jalan Besar cafe trail. We are looking to hire motivated and responsible team players to join our family as servers/baristas.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job scope includes (and is not limited to):</p>\n<p>- table service</p>\n<p>- cashiering</p>\n<p>- oversee cleanliness and order of cafe</p>\n<p>- preparation of coffee, beverages and desserts</p>\n<p>* Onsite training will be provided, no prior experience required. :)</p>\n<p>- Flexible timing, open to working on weekends</p>\n<p>- Shift work available</p>\n<p>- Meals provided</p>\n<p>- Off in-lieu offered for work hours on Public Holidays</p>\n<p>- Cafe is 8 mins walk from either Farrer Park, Lavender or Jalan Besar MRT stations</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Types: Full-time, Part-time, Permanent</p>",
